 largest seller of athletic footwear and apparel in the world where she served as vice president and head of the companys global apparel business from october  to march  from october  to october  ms grossman was president and ceo at polo jeans company then a licensee of polo ralph lauren corporation and from october  to october  vice president of new business development at polo ralph lauren corporation a global leader in the design marketing and distribution of premium lifestyle products from september  to october  ms grossman was president of the chaps ralph lauren division of warnacos menswear and executive vice president of warnaco menswear division from june  to september  ms grossman was vice president of sales and merchandising at tommy hilfiger a global apparel and retail company ms grossman serves as vice chairman for the us fund for unicef and as chairman for the national retail federation nrf she also served as the chairman of the nrf foundation and is a member of the board of directors of bloomin brands in  ms grossman was recognized as one of fast companys most creative people in business and fortunes business person of the year in  forbes magazine named ms grossman one of the worlds  most powerful women ms grossman is a year veteran of the apparel and retail industries and is wellknown for brand strategy and business development she gained significant experience building businesses at nike polo jeans ralph lauren and tommy hilfiger and since becoming chief executive officer or ceo in  has used this experience to help transform and relaunch hsn and to develop and expand the brand and product portfolio ms grossman brings to the board extensive leadership business and management experience including specific experience in brand development ms grossmans service as a director and ceo establishes a critical link between the board and the senior leaders at hsni enabling the board to perform its oversight function with the benefit of managements perspective on the business source hsn inc on    sign up for equilar atlas and view mindy f grossmans full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like mindy f grossman more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in mindy f grossmans network and community follow changes in mindy f grossmans employment and moneyinmotion connect with mindy f grossman through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example mindy f grossman mindy f grossmans connections  sign up now to view mindy f grossmans  connections » jeanne p jackson president product and merchandising nike inc joseph j kadow evp chief legal officer bloomin brands inc thomas e clarke former board member nike inc lisa a letizio board member evine live inc judy a schmeling president cornerstone brands inc and chief operating officer hsn inc elizabeth a smith chairman of the board and chief executive officer bloomin brands inc stephanie a kugelman board member hsn inc stephen k judge former executive vice president and president bonefish grill bloomin brands inc james r craigie chairman and chief executive officer church  dwight co inc eric d sprunk chief operating officer nike inc popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity ltd john j kita evp and cfo a o smith elon r musk ceo and chairman tesla david j oconnor president and ceo the madison square garden company claiborne p deming chairman of the board murphy oil corporation × claim your profile coming soon interested in updating your biography and work history were working on making it happen well email you when this feature is available please enter valid email address done thank you for your interest ok browse executive profiles  a  b  c  d  e  f  g  h  i  j  k  l  m  n  o  p  q  r  s  t  u  v  w  x  y  z equilar homepage equilar atlas equilar insight equilar boardedg