lers patricia mediaretail stars advice go beyond the obvious fortune april    a b c snyder bill how mindy grossman turned around hsn insights by stanford business stanford graduate school of business june    boccaccio katherine and marianne wilson celebrating success retail entrepreneurs honored in annual awards program chain store age november    stelter brian up next reruns from hsn new york times june    a b c d e levy ariel mindy grossmans sellavision success elle february    a b lewis robin qa with mindy grossman ceo hsn the robin report may    a b mindy grossman – profile at fast company  a b c bloomin brands inc appoints two new directors press release bloominbrandscom september    a b lewis robin and michael dart the new rules of retail competing in the worlds toughest marketplace macmillan  pp –  a b goudreau jenna how mindy grossman is transforming hsn forbes august    farrell mike hsn minds the store multichannel news july    a b mindy grossman – profile at forbes  a b s top people in business  mindy grossman fortune  a b most creative people   mindy grossman fast company may    fortune   snapshots – hsn fortune archives  fairchild caroline women ceos in the fortune  by the numbers fortune july    goudreau jenna hsn chief mindy grossman talks women and shopping forbes may    wechsler pat womenled companies perform three times better than the sp  fortune march    thurston susan hsns mindy grossman a hot commodity among retailers tampa bay times july    kapner suzanne and joann s lublin hsn chief turned down job as jc penney wall street journal july    mattioli dana and joann s lublin avon woos hsns mindy grossman for ceo post wall street journal february    hsni – board of directors hsnicom  the container store chairman and ceo kip tindell elected chairman of nrf board of directors states news service january    hsni ceo mindy grossman elected chair of nrf foundation board of directors states news service january    hsni ceo elected to serve another term a